data.text: At Dekker, we're not just designers — we're entrepreneurs. And we're always using that entrepreneurial spirit to solve design problems for our clients. That's why we formed 3AEGREEN Joint Venture together with Bridgers & Paxton and Bohannan Huston, Inc. By partnering with the biggest and best A/E firms in the western United States, we're able to put our heads together to tackle complex design and engineering puzzles in federal government projects. From aerospace complexes to lab buildings to critical infrastructure, the 3AEGREEN Joint Venture designs and builds purpose-driven spaces that help shape our nation. Learn more about the 3AEGREEN Joint Venture! https://www.3aegreen.com/
